title: Aussie miners baffled after spotting bizarre object in the sky above the Pilbara: 'Genuine UFO'

title: Erich von Däniken, ‘Chariots of the Gods?’ author who fueled UFO interest, dies at 90
description: Erich von Däniken, the Swiss author whose books on the alleged extraterrestrial origins of ancient civilizations brought him both fame and scorn, has died at age 90.
